  <Description>
    <Language>en</Language>
    <Type>General</Type>
    <Text>Recreation facilities include a fully equipped health club, an outdoor swimming pool and sundeck on the 6th floor, sauna, Jacuzzi, and a well-equipped fitness centre. For business travellers there is a high-tech business centre with Internet access and exclusive executive lounge.  A choice of meeting rooms and conference facilities are also available. 
(12/07SW)</Text>
  </Description>
  <Description>
    <Language>en</Language>
    <Type>SurroundingArea</Type>
    <Text>The hotel is located in the heart of the colourful Silom Road shopping, business, and gems and jewellery district, next to the river, opposite the Silom Village and within 20 minutes' leisurely walk of the famous Pat Paong entertainment district. Plus the adjacent 2nd-stage expressway and the nearby Surasak sky train station give easy access to the rest of the city.</Text>
  </Description>
  <Description>
    <Language>en</Language>
    <Type>RoomTypes</Type>
    <Text>Rooms are large and similar, decorated in pastel colours. They have a very European feel, and all luxuriously appointed guestrooms and suites are equipped with colour television with in-house video and satellite channels, international direct-dial phone, voice mail and individually controlled air conditioning. Bathrooms are in good condition.</Text>
  </Description>
  <Description>
    <Language>en</Language>
    <Type>PropertyInformation</Type>
    <Text>The hotel is comprised of high-rise twin towers constructed of concrete and glass.</Text>
  </Description>
  <Description>
    <Language>en</Language>
    <Type>DiningFacilities</Type>
    <Text>The hotel offers a choice of restaurants. There is the Indian restaurant on the 6th floor, a Thai restaurant at lobby level and an all-day dining outlet where breakfast is served, also at lobby level. The hotel also has a very warm and cosy pub with nightly entertainment.</Text>
  </Description>
  <Description>
    <Language>en</Language>
    <Type>Short</Type>
    <Text>The lobby is very large and spacious and decorated in spotless white marble. Chandeliers enhance the warm feel. The lobby has plenty of seating areas.</Text>
  </Description>
